spec_data.Name: php-pear-math-biginteger
spec_data.Description:
Supports base-2, base-10, base-16, and base-256 numbers. Uses the GMP or
BCMath extensions, if available, and an internal implementation, otherwise.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:40:05 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Pure-PHP arbitrary precision integer arithmetic library
